{"tid":1927172,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"政府向英美愛爾蘭發紅色外遊警示　抵港人士需強制檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-15T15:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:13:19.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4299796467cc35f3b2cbc46f1aabfed434b6251a","tid":1927172,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"特區政府宣布對愛爾蘭、英國及美國發出紅色外遊警示，由星期四零時零分起，由這三個國家，以及早前已發出紅色外遊警示的埃及，抵港人士需要接受家居強制檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n另外，澳洲宣布當地時間午夜起，所有入境人士要強制檢疫隔離14日。本港多間旅行社隨即取消今日起至下月中或下月底前，出發的澳洲團。<br />\n<br />\n有準備前往澳洲探親的港人，臨時取消行程，批評航空公司未有及時通知乘客，安排失當。\t\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514610-20200315.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514610-20200315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=01668d31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514610-20200315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ac3f722a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514610-20200315.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}